--- WARNING ---

This is an ongoing project. It is still in an early development stage. The IRC Server is not compatible with irc clients yet.

Dependencies:
libpthread, libev

To compile:
make

To generate documentation:
make doc

To run:

./yaircd.out

After that, open up a few terminals and try:
telnet 127.0.0.1 6667

Type in a few messages and check that they are received in every connected terminal. To close your connection, type q